{"tid":989150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【種族歧視】美高中生嘲笑原住民 大喊「建牆！建牆！」","createTime":"2019-01-20T15:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T04:45:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a78fc5a314be0157dcf71a7e54d7c43d9849513d","tid":989150,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190120/large/1547985607_93bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190120%2Flarge%2F1547985607_93bb.jpg&h=4868608b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男學生被拍到向菲利普斯高喊「建牆！」(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n美國一名男學生上周五被拍到在遊行中向一名原住民高喊「建牆！」，影片在網絡瘋傳，各界狠批男生行為嚇人，散播仇恨和不尊重，更有指事件反映總統特朗普帶頭掀起種族歧視。<br />\n一班原住民上周五在華盛頓遊行，在林肯紀念堂外碰上數千名反墮胎遊行人士，包括來自肯塔基州公園山的卡溫頓天主教私立高中男學生。不少學生身穿印有「讓美國再次偉大」(Make America Great Again)的衣服和帽子，他們包圍原住民，高叫口號並嘲笑他們。<br />\n網上流傳片段所見，一名男學生擋在64歲原住民菲利普斯（Nathan Phillips）面前並盯着他看。菲利普斯指當時他正在唱歌，聽到學生高聲喊「建牆！建牆！」，但他認為「這裏是原住民的土地，不應有圍牆，從來都沒有。真希望他們能把精力用來建設國家。」據報他是奧馬哈族(Ohama)長老，亦是越戰老兵。<br />\n卡溫頓的天主教教區和男生就讀的高中發表聯合聲明，向菲利普斯和原住民道歉，譴責該學生行為「違反教會尊重他人的教導」，並指已展開調查，會採取適當行動，不排除將該名學生逐出校。<br />\n美聯社/路透社  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190120/59164473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F59164473&d=EwNonSrI7SgiT3FBTNcE3m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=513aae23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190120%2F59164473&h=2a14dc10\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190120/59164473</a>"},{"pid":"6816641e0bdd5fc1eef015ecaf8d863fe4cee5ef","tid":989150,"uid":20058,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:37:01.000Z","msg":"一班原住民上周五在華盛頓遊行，在林肯紀念堂外碰上數千名<span style=\"color: red;\">反墮胎遊行人士，包括來自肯塔基州公園山的卡溫頓天主教私立高中男學生</span>。不少學生身穿印有「讓美國再次偉大」(Make America Great Again)的衣服和帽子，他們包圍原住民，高叫口號並嘲笑他們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4efe615ce5fee82c91d3a706e584336fde2c110","tid":989150,"uid":31151,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:39:09.000Z","msg":"不少學生身穿印有「讓美國再次偉大」(Make America Great Again)的衣服和帽子<br />\n<br />\n做多左喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d299f673ac6eefbfeb502e1ee72bde625acff48e","tid":989150,"uid":24345,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:39:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/FGoFNV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/FGoFNV</a>"},{"pid":"cd7f9d890337c01648bda31fc21ef54df997c3b6","tid":989150,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:51:40.000Z","msg":"青雲嫂學歷一樣勁,又唔見人唱,唔係搵打手屈9人唔抵得就有道理<br />\n<br />\n10a女不嬲無品睇唔起其他藝員"},{"pid":"b88f0818e6365fae974be5a0301a2d20e6597c5b","tid":989150,"uid":128087,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:44:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.apnews.com/90c35b0e3b1f41abbcb28eef7cf4bd9a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apnews.com%2F90c35b0e3b1f41abbcb28eef7cf4bd9a&d=EwNonSrI7SgiT3FBTNcE3m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9718c38a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apnews.com/90c35b0e3b1f41abbcb28eef7cf4bd9a</a><br />\n個學生話班人係佢地耳仔打鼓<br />\n學生仲保持微笑，無嘲笑班原住民喎<br />\n<br />\n我信學生"},{"pid":"73876db53caa3c51d507be9fd7fafc0262dac62f","tid":989150,"uid":24345,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b88f0818e6365fae974be5a0301a2d20e6597c5b","tid":989150,"uid":128087,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:44:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.apnews.com/90c35b0e3b1f41abbcb28eef7cf4bd9a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apnews.com%2F90c35b0e3b1f41abbcb28eef7cf4bd9a&d=EwNonSrI7SgiT3FBTNcE3m